  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As an action, you enter a parrying stance. Until the beginning of your next turn, you may not make an attack or cast a jutsu that deals damage by any means. However, you increase your Saving throws and AC by +3. If a creature would miss a melee attack against you, you may move them 10 feet in any direction. If they collide with another creature, they're both knocked prone.</p>",
